  "title": "6723 - Personal Trainer (CPT Preferred) – Fitness Industry | Stable Basic Pay | $3–4k",
  "description": "<p><strong>Junior/Senior Personal Trainer</strong></p><p>Salary: Basic: $3,000 - $4000 <strong>(Based on years of experiences) </strong>+ Annual Increment (Based on the staff performance)</p><p>Work location: Near Dhoby Ghaut MRT</p><p>Working days & hours: 5.5 days</p><ul><li>Weekday: Day Shift: 745am-315pm / Night Shift: 145pm-915pm</li><li>Weekends & PH: Day Shift: 745am-115pm / Night Shift: 1245noon-615pm</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Scope:</strong></u></p><ul><li><strong>Guide students how to train effectively:</strong> Coach and motivate students in a safe and highly engaging fitness environment, utilizing unique personal trainer system.</li><li><strong>Coach in a small group setting: </strong>Lead small group training sessions (up to 4 students) to ensure proper exercise technique and students’ safety.</li><li><strong>Foster a positive atmosphere and experience </strong>by motivating and inspiring clients to achieve their full potential by providing ongoing support and encouragement.</li><li><strong>Help coach student beyond the gym </strong>by offering guidance and support through regular check-ins on their daily exercise, nutrition and habits.</li><li><strong>Cultivate and maintain community: </strong>Grow Our Community by contributing to building a strong, supportive community spirit within the gym.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></u></p><p>• Certified Personal Trainer (CPT) or equivalent qualification is preferred</p><p>• Minimum of 1 year of experience in personal training is preferred<br /></p><p></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>📲 Interested candidates, please WhatsApp your resume to: +65 9642 0989 (Han)</strong><br /><strong>📧 Or email your resume to: </strong><a href=\"https://employer.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/jobs/6723-sales-support-customer-care-executive-sgd-2600%E2%80%934000-industrial-services-north-area-post-sales-support-supreme-hr-advisory-a212f1138e3ddd0ad8ec472e0fc6a5d6/view#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">supreme.cc.han@gmail.com</a><strong></strong></p><p><strong>👤 Chaw Chiaw Han | R22106723 🏢 The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</strong></p>",
